      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to say goodbye to this absolute gem, but it's time for a new home! This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It's been pampered since day one, with a spotless interior and a body that shines like it's brand new. If you've been looking for that perfect ride that's been loved and cared for, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have!",
