    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered lineage, maintained to a standard that satisfies the most exacting mechanical scrutiny. The 3.2L high-revving inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a perfectly calibrated double VANOS system, providing linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline. It is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally immaculate, with a documented subframe inspection showing zero stress fractures and original factory cosmoline still present on the undercarriage. All suspension kinematics remain tight, and the cooling system has been proactively addressed to ensure thermal efficiency. This is a collector-grade, turnkey machine for the purist who demands mechanical synchronicity and aesthetic perfection.",
