      "description": "Offered here is a collector-grade example that truly defines the term 'mint.' This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its original factory luster without a single swirl mark or stone chip. The interior remains in showroom state, featuring supple, uncreased leather and that distinct new-car aroma; every button and toggle functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, delivering a seamless driving experience backed by a comprehensive, folder-thick service history. From the pristine undercarriage to the untouched alloy wheels, no detail has been overlooked. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a turnkey, investment-quality vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
